version_description:
[New Function]
<br>1、Add Spring Festival event. The Spring Festival include login rewards, value package, item redeem, summon point redeem, festival limit summon, limit angels skin of Spring Festival;<br>2、Add 50 floors of Sky-tower;<br>3、When viewing other players, increase the viewing of gem information;
<br>
<br>[Optimized Contents]
<br>1、Optimize interface display;
<br>2、Optimize lag and game crash;
<br>3、In achievement quest: change “Main character own a set of X-level enhanced equipments ”to “Own a set of X-level enhanced equipment)

[Optimized Contents]
<br>1.Optimize some language display;
<br>[Bug Fix]
<br>1. Fix the problem that other channel information will appear in the chat language channel;
<br>2. Fix the problem that the "Go" button is invalid in limited points activities
<br>3. Fixed the issue of occasional insufficient VIP level limited during chat;

[New Function]
<br>1. Add 3 game languages: Spanish, German, and Russian. Corresponding in language chat channels;
<br>2. The game server will be divided into three regions: Europe, America, and Asia. Only the Americas region will be opened. Europe and Asia will be opened in the future.
<br>3. Added the function of viewing the history server, which can be viewed in the switching server
<br>[Optimized Contents]
<br>1. Optimize client performance and greatly improve the smoothness of operation and reduce the probability of flashback;
<br>2. Optimize the server performance and greatly improve the network lag problem of the game;
<br>3. Optimize language translation in all languages;
<br>4. Optimize the problem that video ads cannot pop up;
<br>5. Optimize the pop-up rules and rewards of some time-limited gift packages.
<br>【Bug Fix】
<br>1. Fix the problem about blocking players in channel: Players can still see the messages sent by the blocked players in the public chat channel (Only the players in the same server can be blocked).

[New Function]
<br>1. Add new Magic Circle function. In each battle, the team will get an additional attribute bonus according to the number of surviving angels on both sides;
<br>2. Added one-click sweep function on Star Trial ;
<br>3. Unlock Hell-mode in Star Trial;
<br>4. Add gift code function. The gift code will be send through various communities.
<br>[Optimized Contents]
<br>1. In order to adapt to the Magic Circle function, adjust the intensity of dungeon Boss.
<br>2. Optimization Guild BOSS:
<br>a) After you quit the guild, you can not challenge the guild Boss in 24 hours;
<br>b) The guild BOSS consumption honor no longer changes with the BOSS level, consistent be at 2000 honor points;
<br>c) The strength of the guild boss of the same level has increased slightly;
<br>d) Optimization guild boss level changes:
<br>i. The time to defeat the boss is less than or equal to 10 minutes, then the next boss will level up 5 grades;
<br>ii. The time to defeat the boss is greater than 10 minutes, the boss level remains same;
<br>iii. If the boss is not defeated, the boss level is reduced by 10 grades, and the minimum level of guild Boss cannot be lower than Lv40;
<br>3. The angels HP-leech property will be slightly attenuated according to the increase in the number of target skills used;
<br>4. The using of Boss sweeping scrolls no longer increases the number of Boss sweep times. It will be sweeping Boss directly;
<br>5. Adjust chat function, players who are not in the same server can also be blocked;
<br>6. Sapphire store adds bulk purchase function;
<br>7. In the mailbox, after one-click collection, emails without attachments will also become read;
<br>8. During use of the gem pouch, adjust opening 10 times instead of opening 100 times;
<br>9. In battles in the arena, battle reports will save for 10 days.
<br>10. Adjust the maximum rounds of PVP battle is shortened from 50 to 30 rounds. At the end of the round, the defending side (the side with second-attack) wins;
<br>11. Optimize some interface and language display;
<br>[Bug Fix]
<br>1. Fix the problem that damage reflection and real damage will not be calculated by damage reduction;
<br>2. Fix the problem of incorrect prompt when opening the treasure box but the key is insufficient;
<br>3. Fix the problem that the guild board cannot slide when there are too many guild BOSS participants;
<br>4. Fix the problem that the guild chat will be cleared every time when you re-login.

[New Function］
<br>1.Added new grade in angels—SSR+. The original SSR Ra, Hera and Cupid upgraded to SSR+;
<br>2.Added new angels in SSR+: Icarus and Chaos.
<br>3.Added the Angel Guard function, you can use the extra angels to guard, and provide attribute bonus to the angels that have been in the line-up.
<br>[Optimized Contents] 
<br>1.Optimize large part of display in interfaces and texts;
<br>2.Adjustment of summon function;

1. Add Angel upgrade function:
<br>① The level of the angels will no longer follow the player's level, and can be inherited;
<br>② Upgrade requires the using of Angels Exp and Holy core to upgrade;
<br>③ There is an upper limit to the angels’ level, which is related to the quality and awakening level of the angels;
<br>④Angels’ level of registered players will be equal to current players’ level;
<br>2. Added Ocean Day Reprint will be launched from July 17 to 23, including login awards, value-for-money packages, item exchange and point exchange, so stay tuned!
<br>3. Added the Training Vials synthesis function;
<br>4. Add Grow-up Task, and some main story and achievement tasks are adjusted;

[Optimized Contents] 
<br>1. Optimize part of the interface display;
<br>2. The daily ranking rewards of the arena need to be collected manually on the arena leaderboard in next day. The rewards are not collected after the deadline will be issued by email;
<br>[Bug Fix]
<br>1. Fix the problem of too frequent pushes when the adventure is completed in notification center;
<br>2. Fix the problem of incorrect red dot reminders;
<br>3. Fix the issue that the number of summon times must be reached is incorrectly displayed in some players' advanced/elite/epic summons;

[New Contents]
<br>1. Add the new event Lost Sanctuary, including Daily discount, Treasury house, Super gift, Bounty task, so stay tuned!
<br>2. Added battle statistics function;
<br>[Optimized Contents] 
<br>1. Optimize part of the interface and text display;
<br>2. Reforming and upgrade the Sky Tower’s interface;

[New Contents]
<br>1. Add function: Clash of Titans. Players who reach level 35 can sign up. Each competition will be continued for 3 days. Groups setting will be competed based on the highest combat power of players in history. After the competition end, players can get diamonds, holy cores, gold coins and rare avatar frame as rewards based on rankings and points;
<br>2. Added new SSR+ Angel—Heimdall;
<br>[Optimized Contents] 
<br>1. Optimize part of the interface and text display;
<br>2. Optimize the language translation of Portuguese, Spanish, Vietnamese and German;
<br>3. Add a new welfare center module. Nut’s gifts, Ludo and Roulette will be put into this module;
<br>4. Add angels experience and holy core in the Ludo;
<br>5. Main Character adjustment:
<br>①The main character can be awakened by collecting angels to improve the quality or star level. Each time of awaken, main character will unlock or upgrade a skill;
<br>②The main character will be greatly strengthened through awakening;
<br>③Players who registered before the update, the quality of main character will be retained. The awakening condition can be continued after being fulfilled;

